---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const clusters = [
  { label: 'Allergi & astma', href: '/allergi-och-astma/' },
  { label: 'Kemikaliefri städning', href: '/kemikaliefri-stadning/' },
  { label: 'Inomhusluft', href: '/inomhusluft/' },
  { label: 'Mögel & fukt', href: '/mogel-och-fukt/' },
  { label: 'Städtips & rutiner', href: '/stadtips-och-rutiner/' },
  { label: 'Rengöring av apparater', href: '/rengoring-av-apparater/' },
];
---
<footer class="bg-primary-dark text-white mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <a href="/" aria-label="Hälsorent startsida">
            <img src="/halsorent-logo.svg" alt="Hälsorent" class="h-8 w-auto brightness-0 invert" width="166" height="44" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed max-w-md">Oberoende guide om städning och inomhusmiljö för din hälsa. Verifierade råd om allergivänlig städning, kemikaliefria rengöringsmedel, mögel och inomhusluft.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-white/90">Ämnen</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          {clusters.map((c) => (
            <li><a href={c.href} class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">{c.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-white/90">Om oss</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/om-oss/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Om hälsorent</a></li>
          <li><a href="/redaktionen/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Redaktionen</a></li>
          <li><a href="/kontakt/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Kontakt</a></li>
          <li><a href="/redaktionell-policy/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Redaktionell policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sponsrat-innehall/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Sponsrat innehåll</a></li>
          <li><a href="/samarbeta/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Annonsera</a></li>
          <li><a href="/integritetspolicy/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Integritetspolicy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cookies/" class="text-white/70 hover:text-accent-light transition-colors">Cookies</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-white/15 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-white/60">
      <p>© {year} hälsorent.se. Allt innehåll är upphovsrättsskyddat.</p>
      <p>Redaktion: <span class="js-email" data-u="karinholmhalsorent" data-d="proton.me">karinholmhalsorent [at] proton.me</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
